messages.content:
The user wants me to create posters for all interviews, not just Ahmed. They want me to:
1. Make the whole HTML a poster format
2. Think about libraries, JavaScript libraries, icons that could help
3. Make better typography
4. Work in English for now (they'll translate to Arabic later)
5. They said the current design doesn't look that pretty, so I need to improve

Let me think about what would make better posters:
- Better typography libraries (like Google Fonts, typography.js)
- Icon libraries (Font Awesome, Feather Icons, Heroicons)
- CSS frameworks for better design (Tailwind CSS)
- JavaScript libraries for animations or interactions (GSAP, AOS)
- Better layout and visual hierarchy
- More modern, clean design

From the interviews, I can extract key insights:

From Anfal's interview:
- The parametric design approach combining heritage with sustainability
- Using Grasshopper for climate-responsive facades
- The 50+ houses she's designed with insulation
- Her frustration with clients wanting appearance over function
- The biophilic design concept

From Wifaq's interview:
- The reverse engineering approach to problems
- The power shift in consumer awareness (2018)
- The policy paper idea for government subsidies
- The connection between temperature and divorce rates
- The vision for Mosul's 7km expansion

From Laith's interview:
- Trust is everything in Mosul's market
- The visual feedback concept for architects
- Combining heritage with modern sustainability
- The fear graduates have entering the market
- Using interior gardens in 150sqm homes

Let me create a more beautiful, modern poster system.You're right - let me create a much more beautiful poster system! Here's a modern approach using better libraries and design:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Green Building Insights - Interview Posters</title>

    <!-- Google Fonts for better typography -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Crimson+Text:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Phosphor Icons -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/@phosphor-icons/web"></script>

    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #0a0a0a;
            color: #fafafa;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .poster-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .poster {
            aspect-ratio: 3/4;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
            background: #111;
            border: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .poster:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        /* Anfal's Parametric Design Poster */
        .poster-anfal-1 {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #0284c7 100%);
            position: relative;
        }

        .poster-anfal-1::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, transparent 35px, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 35px, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 70px),
                repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent, transparent 35px, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 35px, rgba(255,255,255,.05) 70px);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Wifaq's Systems Thinking Poster */
        .poster-wifaq-1 {
            background: #18181b;
            border: 2px solid #27272a;
        }

        .poster-wifaq-1 .graphic {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 80%;
            height: 80%;
            opacity: 0.1;
        }

        /* Laith's Trust Economy Poster */
        .poster-laith-1 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 100%);
        }

        /* Ahmed's Market Reality Poster */
        .poster-ahmed-1 {
            background: #7c3aed;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .poster-ahmed-1::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -50%;
            right: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        /* Common poster elements */
        .poster-content {
            height: 100%;
            padding: 3rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .poster-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .poster-icon {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .poster-number {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            opacity: 0.6;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .poster-main {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .poster-title {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .poster-quote {
            font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.4;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .poster-insight {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .poster-footer {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .poster-source {
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', monospace;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        /* Special styles for different poster types */
        .dark-poster {
